{"tid":2035173,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實你知唔知國安法 恐怖在 有秘密警察","createTime":"2020-05-25T17:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T02:23:34.000Z","uid":238660,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5e96b11c5cec630740d1aba8b3f7702427e990ab","tid":2035173,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"呢條片以東德時期嘅國安法講緊咩係秘密警察<br />\n<br />\n我講少少歷史先。<br />\n<br />\n國家安全部（德語：Ministerium f&uuml;r Staatssicherheit，縮寫為MfS）係德意志民主共和國嘅國家安全機構，通稱「史塔西」（Stasi)該詞意義為「國安」，來自德語「國家安全」（Staatssicherheit）嘅縮寫，成立於1950年2月8日。值得關注嘅係就連當時嘅東德國家人民軍都有佢地嘅存在，可見其權力之大。<br />\n<br />\n呢班秘密警察係負責壓制國內嘅政治異議者以及擔任執政黨或者政府對國民嘅監視工具，有助於權力嘅鞏固。對反對派、活躍分子以及不同政見者都會採用恐嚇嘅方式加以威脅。<br />\n<br />\n喺國內佢地可以滲透，可以心理騷擾<br />\n喺國外佢地會從事諜報同埋破壞行動<br />\n<br />\nPlease don't  think it easy .<br />\n<br />\n秘密警察用得好固然係維護國家安全，正如美國嘅FBI,CIA <br />\n或者英國嘅MI5同MI6，但係唔好開心得咁快，秘密警察都會係獨裁者嘅迫害工具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=401806b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6fecf5cdac2ac2b3861e01c21bd1de3ea60a43","tid":2035173,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"東德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036c802e99cd7fce5868aaf9420c1bc75558c10b","tid":2035173,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeee